        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>This collection contains FBI files obtained through a FOIA (Freedom of Information Act) request. The files cover FBI observations of Neff and his activities with Communist-affiliated groups and organizations. PLEASE DIRECT FURTHER INQUIRIES TO: peter.filardo@nyu.edu</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Historical/Biographical Note</head>
            <p>Walter Scott Neff was a psychologist and author of several books, including 
                <emph render="italic">Work and Human Behavior</emph>, and was also head of the American Peace Mobilization, a Communist-associated organization, founded in 1940.</p>
